**REQUIREMENTS**

* Windows Vista/7 (XP Untested) or Windows Server 2003/8
* .NET Framework 3.5 


**INSTALLATION**

1. Run bitmoose-gui.exe
1. Click the menu item Service->Install
1. Wait about 5 seconds for the status bar to show "Service Stopped".
1. Configure your miner.
1. On your miner, click the 'Validation' tab, and click the button to make sure it runs ok from a console.
1. Click the menu item Service->Start
>  After the service is started, you should see your miner's output trickling into the miner's status box.

1. Done.
>  You can now log out of windows and let your miner work behind the scenes!
